---
title: Creamy Spaghetti & Organic Meatballs with Scallions & Lemon
description: Spaghetti with cream sauce is one of those simple pleasures. Is there anyone who’d turn down a big bowl of rich, velvety noodles? Surely not, although adding meatballs and a kick of heat and lemon certainly makes it that much more crave-able. Which is exactly what we’re doing: taking a tried-and-true Italian American classic and swapping in a scalliony, peppery, lemon cream sauce topped with tender, savory meatballs. Now that’s amore!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/63d94d4d6e5ae7ecbc060a5c-2baa9fcf.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6539603db8cd6bf4c478fc1e.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/creamy-spaghetti-organic-meatballs-6539603db8cd6bf4c478fc1e
cuisine: Italian
time required: 30 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 960 kcal
  fat: 47 g
  saturated fat: 19 g
  carbohydrates: 90 g
  sugar: 11 g
  protein: 40 g
  fiber: 5 g
  sodium: 1750 mg
servings: 2
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
